商業上，單曲於美國、澳洲、加拿大、愛爾蘭、荷蘭及英國取得了優秀的成績，同時也於其他16個國家榜單中排行前十。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269648/lady-gaga-dances-to-the-top-of-hot-100|title=Lady GaGa Dances To The Top Of Hot 100|first=Jonathan|last=Cohen|work=Billboard|date=2009-01-08|accessdate=2009-01-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140528053527/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269648/lady-gaga-dances-to-the-top-of-hot-100|archivedate=2014-05-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/australia_singles_top_50/2008/38|title=Australian ARIA Singles Chart|date=2008-06-15|work=Australian Recording Industry Association|publisher=aCharts.us|accessdate=2009-04-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111203214516/http://acharts.us/australia_singles_top_50/2008/38|archivedate=2011-12-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/canada_singles_top_100/2008/34|title=Canadian Hot 100|date=2008-08-23|work=Billboard|publisher=aCharts.us|accessdate=2009-04-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110924172505/http://acharts.us/canada_singles_top_100/2008/34|archivedate=2011-09-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/uk_singles_top_75/2009/03|title=UK Singles Chart|date=2009-01-11|publisher=The Official Charts Company|accessdate=2009-04-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090118170611/http://acharts.us/uk_singles_top_75/2009/03|archivedate=2009-01-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/song/35829|title=Lady Gaga – "Just Dance" on world charts|publisher=aCharts.us|accessdate=2009-06-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090218151824/http://acharts.us/song/35829|archivedate=2009-02-18}}</ref> 歌曲獲得[[第51屆葛萊美獎|第51屆葛萊美獎]]「最佳舞曲錄製類」提名，但最後輸給了[[電子樂|電子樂]]團體[[傻瓜龐克|傻瓜龐克]]的歌曲《{{tsl|en|Harder, Better, Faster, Stronger|更努力 更好 更快 更強}}》(Harder, Better, Faster, Stronger) 。.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1600678/20081204/coldplay.jhtml|title=Lil Wayne, Coldplay Lead Grammy Nominations|date=2008-12-04|accessdate=2009-04-27|last=Harris|first=Chris|publisher=MTV News|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090308092135/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1600678/20081204/coldplay.jhtml|archivedate=2009-03-08}}</ref>

《[[撲克臉_(女神卡卡歌曲)|撲克臉]]》(Poker Face) 作為第2張單曲，也獲得了一致好評，其中多數評論家皆稱讚歌曲中帶有機器人音效的Hook以及副歌。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://login.vnuemedia.com/bbbiz/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003943244|title=Single Reviews: Poker Face|last=Williams|first=Chris|date=2009-02-28|accessdate=2009-02-28|work=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091119051710/http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/detailview.html?KEY=UICS-9104|archivedate=2009-11-19}}</ref> 這張單曲釋出時幾乎在所有的國家登榜首冠軍，並達到了比《舞力全開》更完美的成就。<ref name="pair">{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269065/lady-gaga-draws-a-pair-of-no-1s|title=Lady GaGa Draws A Pair Of No. 1s|last=Pietroluongo|first=Silvio|date=2009-04-01|accessdate=2009-04-01|work=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922174639/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269065/lady-gaga-draws-a-pair-of-no-1s|archivedate=2013-09-22}}</ref> 《撲克臉》也成為了卡卡生涯中連續第2張冠軍單曲。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269058/lady-gaga-scores-hot-100-milestone-with-poker-face|title=Lady GaGa Scores Hot 100 Milestone With 'Poker Face'|first=Ayala|last=Ben-Yehuda|first2=Silvio|last2=Pietroluongo|date=2009-04-02|accessdate=2009-04-02|work=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925053438/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269058/lady-gaga-scores-hot-100-milestone-with-poker-face|archivedate=2013-09-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/song/37371|title=Lady Gaga – "Poker Face" on world charts|publisher=aCharts.us|accessdate=2009-06-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220120023/http://acharts.us/song/37371|archivedate=2009-02-20}}</ref> 2009年12月2日，《撲克臉》在[[第52屆葛萊美獎|第52屆葛萊美獎]]獲提名為「年度歌曲」以及「年度製作」，並贏得了「最佳舞曲錄製」。<ref name="grammy" />

《[[嗯，嗯（無話可說）|嗯，嗯（無話可說）]]》(Eh, Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say)) 於澳大利亞、紐西蘭、瑞典以及丹麥作為第3張─於法國做為第4張單曲釋出。這首歌與先前不同，獲得「褒貶不一」的評論。在一部分評論家稱讚單曲90年代{{tsl|en| Europop |歐洲流行}}的曲風時，另一部分則批評其曲風使得專輯的派對性質滯留不前。 <ref name="popmatters" /> 單曲無法於澳洲及紐西蘭取得像先前兩張單曲的好成績，僅排行第15及第9名。同時也於瑞典及法國排行第2和第7名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/song/41262|title=Lady Gaga – "Eh, Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say)" on world charts|publisher=aCharts.us|accessdate=2009-06-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221000748/http://acharts.us/song/41262|archivedate=2009-02-21}}</ref>

《[[愛情遊戲|愛情遊戲]]》(Love Game) 於美國、加拿大及部分歐洲國家作為第3─於澳洲、紐西蘭及英國作為第4張單曲發行。單曲抓耳的曲調以及「我想要騎上你迪斯可棒」的Hook獲得了評論性的讚揚。<ref name="bbc">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/music/reviews/f6bd|title=Lady GaGa The Fame Review|first=Talia|last=Kraines|date=2009-01-09|accessdate=2009-04-06|publisher=BBC News|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090405210433/http://www.bbc.co.uk/music/reviews/f6bd|archivedate=2009-04-05}}</ref> 單曲於美國、澳洲及加拿大等部分國家排行前10，並於其他國家排行前20。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/268458/lady-gaga-takes-two-top-10-spots-on-billboards-hot-100|title=Lady GaGa Takes Two Top 10 Spots On Billboard's Hot 100|last=Ben-Yehuda|first=Ayala|first2=Silvio|last2=Pietroluongo|date=2009-06-04|work=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628141531/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/268458/lady-gaga-takes-two-top-10-spots-on-billboards-hot-100|archivedate=2014-06-28|accessdate=2018-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/song/37372|title=Lady Gaga – "LoveGame" on world charts|publisher=aCharts.us|accessdate=2009-06-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221043317/http://acharts.us/song/37372|archivedate=2009-02-21}}</ref>

《[[愛情狗仔|愛情狗仔]]》(Paparazzi) 於英國及愛爾蘭作為第3、於美國做為第4並於其他國家作為第5張單曲於2009年7月6日發行。<ref name="greenday">{{cite news|url=http://login.vnuemedia.com/bbbiz/content_display/industry/e3i0cc7a863b3935049010f19d5f0d4c2fb|title=Green Day Rises To European Chart Summit|last=Sexton|first=Paul|date=2009-05-28|accessdate=2009-05-29|work=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091119051710/http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/detailview.html?KEY=UICS-9104|archivedate=2009-11-19}}</ref> 單曲於澳洲、加拿大、愛爾蘭及英國排行前5。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/song/43424|title=Lady Gaga – "Paparazzi" on world charts|publisher=aCharts.us|accessdate=2009-06-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100917072656/http://acharts.us/song/43424|archivedate=2010-09-17}}</ref> 於美國排行排行前10。單曲饒富趣味、適合夜店播送的性質被給予了肯定並被認為是專輯中最難忘及敘述的歌曲。<ref name="broward" /> 單曲的音樂影片以為電影的方式拍攝，其中卡卡飾演一名被丈夫謀害失敗但為此殞落的明星。結局中，她完成了她的復仇並找回了以往的名氣及聲望。<ref name="mtvleak">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1612375/20090529/lady_gaga.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga Angry That Epic 'Paparazzi' Video Leaked|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|date=2009-05-29|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2009-06-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601043524/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1612375/20090529/lady_gaga.jhtml|archivedate=2009-06-01}}</ref>

==超人氣魔神==
{{Main|超人氣魔神}}
《超人氣魔神》是專輯《超人氣》的再版，2009年11月18日發行。原先計畫於作為《超人氣》的豪華版曲目，但新視鏡公司於後決定於部分地區釋出八首曲目一組的獨立[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]。這決定起於卡卡認為再發行《超人氣》的資金太過昂貴、並表示這些歌曲[[陰陽|陰與陽]]的概念與《超人氣》的概念大相逕庭。雖然該專輯的豪華版仍舊包含了整張《超人氣》的曲目，但在曲目編排上改以獨立雙碟的方式發行。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626134/20091112/lady_gaga.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga Is 'Honoring' Fans With Cheaper Fame Monster|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|date=2009-11-12|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2009-11-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091115104953/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626134/20091112/lady_gaga.jhtml|archivedate=2009-11-15}}</ref> 專輯本身象徵著名氣的黑暗面，以卡卡於2008至2009年巡迴世界演出的經驗為主軸，透過隱喻將這些負面經驗擬化為怪獸。專輯封面{{tsl|en|Hedi Slimane|海迪．斯里曼}}拍攝，為了在形象上採用哥德式風格，卡卡甚至與唱片公司產生衝突。該作品的靈感源自[[哥德搖滾|哥德式音樂]]及時尚走秀。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/lady-gaga-returns-with-8-new-songs-on-the-fame-monster-63780227.html|title=Lady Gaga Returns With 8 New Songs on 'The Fame Monster'|last=Release|first=Press|date=2009-10-08|publisher=[[Yahoo!_Finance|Yahoo! Finance]]|accessdate=2009-10-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091011005910/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/lady-gaga-returns-with-8-new-songs-on-the-fame-monster-63780227.html|archivedate=2009-10-11}}</ref>

現代評論家大多給予專輯「一致好評」，並稱讚收錄其中的曲目，例如《[[羅曼死|羅曼死]]》(Bad Romance) 、《[[電話_(歌曲)|電話]]》(Telephone) 及《[[在黑暗中漫舞_(歌曲)|在黑暗中漫舞]]》(Dance in The Dark) 等。<ref name="independent">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/album-lady-gaga-the-fame-monster-polydor-1825787.html|title=Album: Lady Gaga, The Fame Monster (Polydor)|last=Price|first=Simon|date=2009-11-22|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|accessdate=2009-11-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091124085219/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/album-lady-gaga-the-fame-monster-polydor-1825787.html|archivedate=2009-11-24}}</ref> 在部分國家專輯榜會將《超人氣魔神》與《超人氣》合併為同一名次，而其他像美國、加拿大和日本等，則會將兩張專輯名次分開計算。在它於主流市場中排行前十時，她宣布宣傳《超人氣魔神》的巡演─魔神巡迴演唱會，將會於2009年11月27日開始。<ref name="bbannounceball">{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267048/lady-gaga-unveils-monster-ball-tour-dates-the-fame-monster-tracklist|title=Lady Gaga Announces 'The Monster Ball'|accessdate=2009-10-15|date=2009-10-15|last=Herrera|first=Monica|work=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223023430/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267048/lady-gaga-unveils-monster-ball-tour-dates-the-fame-monster-tracklist|archivedate=2016-02-23}}</ref> 並持續到2011年春季。

